{"title":"弄潮儿——致改革者","authors":["牟超日"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":3,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"弄潮儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——致改革者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牟超日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并不是在梦中，他们不会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灵魂早已漫过堤岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酝酿了很久很久"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任何劝说都是多余"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命不轰轰烈烈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最好去乘永远搁浅的船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不需颠簸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溅不进半点苦涩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"准备触一夜间突升的礁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渴望潮头闯出新路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深知会撞破舟筏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"救生衣也只不过是装饰品"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任其自然，努力驾驭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不信命运有预定的轨迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弄潮儿注定沉浮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢上波峰，能忍浪谷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不怕猛然间被摔进滩涂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"糊一脸泥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任观潮者指点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本性难移"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是淹没了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没想过树一块墓碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能成鬼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要为后来者呐喊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不敢祈求巨浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溅湿所有的灵魂"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}